{"tid":121553,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"係酒吧度差D俾個女仔呃走部電話 手足們小心D","createTime":"2017-02-15T10:38:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-15T15:21:21.000Z","uid":84102,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"69102f28e5a9ebe693819ba31642dc9efa756ba0","tid":121553,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T10:38:17.000Z","msg":"話說尋晚收工自己一個落吧飲酒<br />\n飲飲下突然間有個女仔行埋黎 一開口就話：「Hello , 可唔可以俾電話我呀」 我望一望佢 頂盡廿歲 幾靚女 白白淨 <br />\n果下真係好慶 好人好姐想呃人部電話 <br />\n<br />\n我就話：「咁大個人你自己連電話都無部咩」<br />\n<br />\n佢個表情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 話：「唔係呀⋯⋯我想要你電話呀⋯⋯」<br />\n<br />\n我果下慶到仆街：「俾埋個銀包你好無！」<br />\n<br />\n之後佢見呃我唔到就面懵懵走撚左去<br />\n<br />\n而家D人，好眉好貌學人做賊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3428a5f94e855f18cb320d4b677617fadb48542b","tid":121553,"uid":42429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T10:39:07.000Z","msg":"幽默感依家野。。。"},{"pid":"4c4ffd35aa426d61393cd1d9bc181a66a0e78d4e","tid":121553,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T10:39:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69ead5668d63c503ab741164d331e029cff2fff0","tid":121553,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T10:42:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幽默感依家野。。。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6d4710303211a8ae49086680bdcc7d2915a6a86","tid":121553,"uid":47279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T10:49:18.000Z","msg":"好多年前既高登&gt;好多年公海&gt;幾年前高登&gt;重覆唔知幾多&gt;唔知幾多個公海&gt;連登<br />\n<br />\n好似係"},{"pid":"394f40dad8f86abf5dd3115fce37a5122601983f","tid":121553,"uid":27777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T10:54:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/15/185411_02ce4ec4177b128355